title: Frank Lloyd Wright Socks—Coonley Playhouse/Red
description:
Sit back, relax, and put your feet up. Way up! You’ll want everyone to see this fancy footwear. Made of a soft and sturdy cotton, nylon and spandex blend, these socks are woven with a design adapted from Frank Lloyd Wright’s®(American, 1867–1959) art glass window triptych in the Avery Coonley Playhouse. Designed in New York, produced in Columbia. 

3 ½ x 10 in.
